{"tid":746152,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［集思廣益］如何杜絕五毛/大陸仔在香港網絡世界生存？","createTime":"2018-07-17T10:46:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-17T13:02:09.000Z","uid":12068,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"0261536de024cad6c3c5fd1046766781307a7f52","tid":746152,"uid":12068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T10:46:45.000Z","msg":"而家五毛氾濫境況，大家有目共睹，差不多開個公廁屙屎環境廁評，都可以有隻五毛話支那啲廁所高香港幾班，好屙啲 吧吧吧⋯⋯⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n自問網齡唔淺（唔是扮老海鮮），但而家兒登身為香港網上嘅最後一塊淨土，五毛問題都咁嚴重，再咁落去，我都唔係好想繼續上&hellip;正如香港沉淪一樣，我好想救好想改變，但根本改變唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n以前高登五毛比例可能係 十比二咁，而家連登個比例根本已經去到 十比七甚至更甚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> （有點根本唔係職業五毛，而係呢十年八載落嚟嘅支那仔自己護主，本人稱之為天然五毛）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n究竟連仔你有無諗過點解決？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 求鳩其就有個連登account <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n大家有無好意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff9493121c45e81bd3529ebce104fed28387cd07","tid":746152,"uid":31637,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T10:49:49.000Z","msg":"顯示中國ip 囉"},{"pid":"bba7bc638a11ff155e2026289ab0b5d577e810bc","tid":746152,"uid":85659,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T10:58:01.000Z","msg":"承認香港祖國是英國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8742036c25150160fc4a594b1cddfaf70491c2a","tid":746152,"uid":163826,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T11:09:16.000Z","msg":"你係連登開呢d post係冇用架。我都開過呢D POST但太多五毛，AA，同未出齊毛既小朋友。"},{"pid":"87554d3895fb8724f303d0d13e05bd1d4f590b89","tid":746152,"uid":53026,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T12:21:57.000Z","msg":"認真，搞多幾個連登新高登，食窮維穩費，即係好似近排共匪話搞退休金咁。"},{"pid":"5